#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:2 2f24e39cab1e48aaa740f4de7c9205c4
msgid "Basics & Visualization"
msgstr "基础与可视化"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:4 4c34dcbdf51f41e58b0623faa5804022
msgid ""
"Four short scripts in ``examples/basics/`` that visualize the building "
"blocks of FEM in TensorMesh: where interpolation nodes sit on the reference "
"element, what the shape functions look like, how internal node numbering "
"compares to Gmsh / VTK, and what the mesh generators produce. None of these "
"scripts solve a PDE — they exist to make the underlying objects tangible and"
" to sanity-check the conventions used elsewhere in the library."
msgstr ""
"``examples/basics/`` 中有四个简短脚本，用于可视化 TensorMesh "
"中有限元方法的基础构件：插值节点在参考单元上的分布位置、形函数的形态、内部节点编号与 Gmsh / VTK "
"编号的对比，以及网格生成器的产物。这些脚本都不求解偏微分方程——它们的作用是让底层对象变得直观可见，并对库中其他地方使用的约定进行合理性检查。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:12 cf6854a0a2ec43db89b14cdf2dec55bc
msgid ""
"If you are reading this page after the "
":doc:`../user_guide/elements_and_quadrature` user-guide page, treat these "
"scripts as the picture book that goes with it."
msgstr ""
"如果你是在阅读 :doc:`../user_guide/elements_and_quadrature` "
"用户指南页面之后才来到本页，可以把这些脚本当作与之配套的图册。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:18 7af96709fffc49c08f968005966ddb06
msgid "Interpolation nodes"
msgstr "插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:20 669f63eedabf4f909354760464590506
msgid ""
"``examples/basics/basis.py`` plots the spatial distribution of interpolation"
" (Lagrange) nodes on the reference element for all seven element classes — "
":class:`~tensormesh.Line`, :class:`~tensormesh.Triangle`, "
":class:`~tensormesh.Quadrilateral`, :class:`~tensormesh.Tetrahedron`, "
":class:`~tensormesh.Hexahedron`, :class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid`, "
":class:`~tensormesh.Prism` — at orders 1 through 4. The driver is a one-"
"liner per element class:"
msgstr ""
"``examples/basics/basis.py`` 绘制全部七种单元类——:class:`~tensormesh.Line`\\ 、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.Triangle`\\ 、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Quadrilateral`\\ 、\\"
" :class:`~tensormesh.Tetrahedron`\\ 、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Hexahedron`\\ "
"、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid`\\ 、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Prism`——在 1 至 4 "
"阶下，参考单元上插值（拉格朗日）节点的空间分布。每个单元类的驱动代码只有一行："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:28 11ff53dc9cd44f639603f093ebbeae05
msgid "examples/basics/basis.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/basics/basis.py（核心）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:42 3084a8d4f7a64b2d813abd6c32d93fe0
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The number of basis points grows quickly with order: :math:`(p+1)^d` for "
"tensor elements, :math:`\\binom{p+d}{d}` for simplex elements. Knowing where"
" they sit is the first sanity check when something goes wrong with a higher-"
"order solve."
msgstr ""
"基函数节点的数量随阶数迅速增长：张量单元为 :math:`(p+1)^d`\\ ，单纯形单元为 :math:`\\binom{p+d}{d}`\\ "
"。当高阶求解出现问题时，了解这些节点的位置是首要的合理性检查。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:48 418bcc35b15746d99b7b1ca0087de060
msgid ""
"The seven panels below show the Lagrange-node layout for every supported "
"element class at orders 1–4. Each panel reads left-to-right by order; node "
"indices match the internal ``element.get_basis(order)`` ordering."
msgstr ""
"下面七幅图展示了每种受支持单元类在 1–4 阶下的拉格朗日节点布局。每幅图按阶数从左到右排列；节点索引与内部 "
"``element.get_basis(order)`` 的编号一致。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:53 25d72062ed1944e2a9994839e5415838
msgid "Line element interpolation nodes"
msgstr "线单元插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:57 5cdb0c47c76443789c5809f7b79edfb0
msgid "``Line`` element — lexicographic ordering on :math:`[0, 1]`."
msgstr "``Line`` 单元——在 :math:`[0, 1]` 上的字典序编号。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:59 07ce9382839b4529b66023c5e7541c31
msgid "Triangle element interpolation nodes"
msgstr "三角形单元插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:63 e4bd30952c404459a246a72e21299faa
msgid ""
"``Triangle`` element — simplex ordering with vertex nodes first, then edge "
"nodes, then interior nodes."
msgstr "``Triangle`` 单元——单纯形编号，先排顶点节点，再排边节点，最后排内部节点。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:66 117bf5a443964cb997490e6573bf6b53
msgid "Quadrilateral element interpolation nodes"
msgstr "四边形单元插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:70 beec064022d443869859217abb5e2cf0
msgid "``Quadrilateral`` element — tensor-product Lagrange nodes."
msgstr "``Quadrilateral`` 单元——张量积拉格朗日节点。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:72 4d8c1484662e48e2bc352c2cfa952ded
msgid "Tetrahedron element interpolation nodes"
msgstr "四面体单元插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:76 213411cdb20f445184c8c07414235046
msgid "``Tetrahedron`` element — 3D simplex."
msgstr "``Tetrahedron`` 单元——三维单纯形。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:78 22c1d04e65c945669e815bf425eee35c
msgid "Hexahedron element interpolation nodes"
msgstr "六面体单元插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:82 bdf7d6d398c54f5486cd98c9865d79c3
msgid "``Hexahedron`` element — 3D tensor product."
msgstr "``Hexahedron`` 单元——三维张量积。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:84 f4bf72081cf2496cbfe1e89d735fb3f3
msgid "Prism element interpolation nodes"
msgstr "三棱柱单元插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:88 94f7b6919371471fac3b2477da8d57a5
msgid "``Prism`` (wedge) element — triangle :math:`\\times` line."
msgstr "``Prism``\\ （楔形）单元——三角形 :math:`\\times` 线。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:90 7bb30257ddba428bbe8043a9df83f2aa
msgid "Pyramid element interpolation nodes"
msgstr "四棱锥单元插值节点"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:94 cff136b8874b4391beca13dfb2ccc29f
msgid "``Pyramid`` element — square base, apex at the top."
msgstr "``Pyramid`` 单元——方形底面，顶点在上方。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:98 5c54c58f0c92481db0df62e0195cd36e
msgid "Shape functions"
msgstr "形函数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:100
#: a9dda4c3f2424a5cae979117ef0e9529
msgid ""
"``examples/basics/basis_fn.py`` plots the polynomial shape functions "
"themselves. For 1D elements they appear as curves on :math:`[-1,1]`; for 2D "
"elements as 3D surfaces on the reference triangle or square; for 3D elements"
" one figure per order with a slice through the volume."
msgstr ""
"``examples/basics/basis_fn.py`` 绘制多项式形函数本身。对于一维单元，它们表现为 :math:`[-1,1]` "
"上的曲线；对于二维单元，表现为参考三角形或方形上的三维曲面；对于三维单元，每个阶数对应一幅图，并带有一个穿过体积的切片。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:106
#: 65f36582f43046c68321c76b9a3a29f9
msgid ""
"The script uses ``element.get_basis_fns(order)``, the same call "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` makes during assembly. If a shape "
"function looks wrong here, it is wrong in your assembled matrix too."
msgstr ""
"该脚本使用 ``element.get_basis_fns(order)``\\ ，这与 "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` "
"在装配过程中所做的调用相同。如果某个形函数在这里看起来有误，那么它在你装配出的矩阵中同样有误。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:111
#: 4ccfb55de7884ec597c53c39c8ccf0aa
msgid ""
"In principle ``get_basis_fns`` accepts **arbitrary** polynomial order — "
"there is no hard cap baked into the API. The figures below show 1D and 2D "
"shape functions at orders 1–3 (plus the full composite view) and 3D shape "
"functions at order 1; higher 3D orders are equally available, they are "
"simply omitted here for space."
msgstr ""
"原则上 ``get_basis_fns`` 接受\\ **任意**\\ 多项式阶数——API 中并未内置硬性上限。下面的图展示了 1–3 "
"阶的一维和二维形函数（外加完整的合成视图），以及 1 阶的三维形函数；更高阶的三维形函数同样可用，这里仅出于篇幅原因略去。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:120
#: ab186ccd23164cad8270e540d353d19f
msgid ""
"Although arbitrary orders are supported, very high orders (in practice "
":math:`\\geq 4` for some element classes) are evaluated through a "
"Vandermonde matrix that becomes increasingly ill-conditioned with order. The"
" script may print a numerical warning in that regime. The returned values "
"are still usable — but if you see those warnings during a real solve, drop "
"to a lower order or switch to a different element class. For most FEM "
"workloads orders 1–3 are the sweet spot."
msgstr ""
"虽然支持任意阶数，但很高的阶数（实际中某些单元类在 :math:`\\geq 4` "
"时）是通过范德蒙德（Vandermonde）矩阵求值的，而该矩阵随阶数升高会变得越来越病态。在此情形下脚本可能会打印数值警告。返回的值仍然可用——但如果你在真实求解过程中看到这些警告，请降低阶数或改用其他单元类。对于大多数有限元方法工作负载，1–3"
" 阶是最佳选择。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:131
#: f081d9449e2841a783694cafe36cdd54
msgid "1D and 2D shape functions"
msgstr "一维与二维形函数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:133
#: 84e2ddc07f7a43a19c1ce7c3ed9eac74
