#: 02b152edb85c4362946c7c282e7659db
msgid ""
"``Line`` shape functions at orders 1–3, plus a composite view of the highest"
" order. Stars mark the interpolation nodes."
msgstr "1–3 阶的 ``Line`` 形函数，以及最高阶的合成视图。星号标记插值节点。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:140
#: cc1016ce91264da388b24a27572ce977
