msgstr "1、2、3 阶的三角形形函数曲面"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:144
#: 67f0e9fea4674be9bfc55e481a7c552e
msgid ""
"``Triangle`` shape functions plotted as 3D surfaces over the reference "
"triangle."
msgstr "``Triangle`` 形函数，以参考三角形上的三维曲面形式绘制。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:147
#: 1935274ff3334d2688d8631c634867e4
msgid "Quadrilateral shape function surfaces at orders 1, 2, 3"
msgstr "1、2、3 阶的四边形形函数曲面"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:151
#: de52851e609f4b4789a0f0f93f0a39e2
msgid "``Quadrilateral`` shape functions on the reference square."
msgstr "参考方形上的 ``Quadrilateral`` 形函数。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:155
#: 677e9521205b417cb52fc19d91e9c290
msgid "3D shape functions (order 1)"
msgstr "三维形函数（1 阶）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:157
#: e1f76bc2520041388fd0d9f76d784cad
msgid ""
"For 3D elements the script renders one volumetric figure per element / order"
" combination; only the order-1 panels are shown below. The full set "
"(including orders 2–4) lands in "
"``examples/basics/output/<element>/<order>.png`` after running the script."
msgstr ""
"对于三维单元，脚本为每个单元 / 阶数组合渲染一幅体绘制图；下面仅展示 1 阶的图。运行脚本后，完整集合（包括 2–4 阶）会保存到 "
"``examples/basics/output/<element>/<order>.png``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:163
#: 474937e5fb9144f986b931fcfc7e763a
msgid "Hexahedron order-1 shape functions"
msgstr "六面体 1 阶形函数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:167
#: 5fb819b757ca4a8d9e3ff4739005a62d
msgid ""
"``Hexahedron`` order-1 shape functions — eight trilinear basis functions, "
"one per vertex."
msgstr "``Hexahedron`` 1 阶形函数——八个三线性基函数，每个顶点对应一个。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:170
#: 7e8d7728f09d409dba34a8f07871883d
msgid "Tetrahedron order-1 shape functions"
msgstr "四面体 1 阶形函数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:174
#: 517c1f9e743a4d619d0daf13a2f1bc31
msgid ""
"``Tetrahedron`` order-1 shape functions — four barycentric coordinates."
msgstr "``Tetrahedron`` 1 阶形函数——四个重心坐标。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:177
#: 799d2df57d05433795ad941b10a264fe
