msgstr "三棱柱 1 阶形函数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:181
#: 07fa1d670f1e40a29ac54c9a6dbc3cb2
msgid ""
"``Prism`` order-1 shape functions — six basis functions, one per vertex of "
"the triangular prism."
msgstr "``Prism`` 1 阶形函数——六个基函数，三棱柱每个顶点对应一个。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:184
#: 137d66794e2a4ea1a5585361adbddcab
msgid "Pyramid order-1 shape functions"
msgstr "四棱锥 1 阶形函数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:188
#: c6a90022382a4479975f118da72b6f87
msgid ""
"``Pyramid`` order-1 shape functions — five basis functions, one per vertex."
msgstr "``Pyramid`` 1 阶形函数——五个基函数，每个顶点对应一个。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:195
#: 5d76a3f5bb0c467390f9e6d43059b028
msgid "Gmsh / VTK ↔ TensorMesh node ordering"
msgstr "Gmsh / VTK ↔ TensorMesh 节点编号"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:197
#: e1515a0d3b6b44dc8e10cf64aea718ff
msgid ""
"``examples/basics/element_gallery.py`` puts TensorMesh's internal node "
"numbering side-by-side with the Gmsh / VTK convention, for 2D and 3D "
"elements at orders 2–4. The output is a two-row plot per element type: top "
"row is the TensorMesh / FEniCS-style ordering; bottom row is the Gmsh / VTK "
"ordering."
msgstr ""
"``examples/basics/element_gallery.py`` 将 TensorMesh 的内部节点编号与 Gmsh / VTK "
"约定并排展示，覆盖 2–4 阶的二维和三维单元。输出为每种单元类型一幅两行图：上一行是 TensorMesh / FEniCS 风格的编号；下一行是 "
"Gmsh / VTK 编号。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:203
#: 4710a902ff3f408b88275fd97559d772
msgid ""
"This is the visual companion to the ``reorder=True`` story in "
":doc:`../user_guide/meshes`: when you load a Gmsh ``.msh`` or write a VTU "
"through meshio, TensorMesh applies the inverse permutation returned by "
"``element.get_gmsh_permutation(order)`` so internal connectivity always uses"
" the same convention. If you ever question which numbering a particular "
"array is in, this script makes it obvious."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../user_guide/meshes` 中关于 ``reorder=True`` 的内容由本脚本提供可视化配套说明：当你加载 Gmsh "
"的 ``.msh`` 文件或通过 meshio 写出 VTU 时，TensorMesh 会施加 "
"``element.get_gmsh_permutation(order)`` "
"返回的逆置换，从而使内部连接性始终采用同一约定。如果你不确定某个数组采用的是哪种编号，这个脚本能让答案一目了然。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:211
#: 258c87e5576149b88434974af31a5ad6
msgid ""
"Four representative comparisons are shown below — one per element family. "
"The remaining element types (line, prism, pyramid) follow the same two-row "
"layout; the full set lives in ``examples/basics/output/element_gallery/``."
msgstr ""
"下面展示了四个代表性对比——每个单元族一个。其余单元类型（线、三棱柱、四棱锥）采用相同的两行布局；完整集合位于 "
"``examples/basics/output/element_gallery/``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:216
#: 16a4d2cd96b54b5191001058fbbf7719
msgid "Triangle node ordering, TensorMesh vs Gmsh/VTK, orders 2-4"
msgstr "三角形节点编号，TensorMesh 与 Gmsh/VTK 对比，2-4 阶"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:220
#: 2e2addf927bf4eb097a998fdeec25efe
msgid ""
"``Triangle`` — top row: TensorMesh / FEniCS ordering; bottom row: Gmsh / VTK"
" ordering."
msgstr "``Triangle``——上一行：TensorMesh / FEniCS 编号；下一行：Gmsh / VTK 编号。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:223
#: 4ef5f8bbc6874bffad70f23800c5bdf9
msgid "Quadrilateral node ordering, TensorMesh vs Gmsh/VTK, orders 2-4"
msgstr "四边形节点编号，TensorMesh 与 Gmsh/VTK 对比，2-4 阶"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:227
#: 17c3cf2815084a2eaaa3176e7047fdd1
msgid ""
"``Quadrilateral`` — note that the TensorMesh layout is lexicographic, while "
"Gmsh's order-3 / order-4 quad layouts spiral around the boundary."
msgstr ""
"``Quadrilateral``——注意 TensorMesh 的布局是字典序的，而 Gmsh 的 3 阶 / 4 阶四边形布局是沿边界螺旋排列的。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:231
#: 157848663d4347ec84ce02145df3291e
msgid "Tetrahedron node ordering, TensorMesh vs Gmsh/VTK, orders 2-4"
msgstr "四面体节点编号，TensorMesh 与 Gmsh/VTK 对比，2-4 阶"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:235
#: 6206563569ce41389a467715e690b7e8
msgid ""
"``Tetrahedron`` — vertex / edge / face / interior groupings are preserved "
"across both orderings, only the indices within each group differ."
msgstr "``Tetrahedron``——顶点 / 边 / 面 / 内部的分组在两种编号下都保持一致，仅各组内的索引有所不同。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:239
#: 25fc1558f3344d96be7e4c6307564bf2
msgid "Hexahedron node ordering, TensorMesh vs Gmsh/VTK, orders 2-4"
msgstr "六面体节点编号，TensorMesh 与 Gmsh/VTK 对比，2-4 阶"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:243
#: 9a3b02c0222048ec8ad05a26b02ca7e9
msgid ""
"``Hexahedron`` — the largest discrepancy in the gallery, since Gmsh's hex "
"ordering walks along edges while TensorMesh's is plain lexicographic."
msgstr "``Hexahedron``——本画廊中差异最大的情形，因为 Gmsh 的六面体编号沿边游走，而 TensorMesh 的是单纯的字典序。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:251
#: 3dcbc09e7be34e4db5e2d1b4e0de158b
msgid "Mesh generation gallery"
msgstr "网格生成画廊"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:253
#: f29eb8ffb10c4ad8af02d983237c8593
msgid ""
"``examples/basics/plot_mesh.py`` is the picture catalog of what TensorMesh's"
" mesh tools can produce, plus a few visualization helpers from "
":mod:`tensormesh.visualization`:"
msgstr ""
"``examples/basics/plot_mesh.py`` 是 TensorMesh 网格工具产物的图册，并附带 "
":mod:`tensormesh.visualization` 中的几个可视化辅助函数："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:257
#: 37d2472c7463400ca326ea5c7c612a17
msgid ""
"**Built-in primitives** — rectangle (triangle and quadrilateral), cube "
"(tetrahedral and hexahedral, the latter with quadratic basis), and a unit "
"disk via :class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen`."
msgstr ""
"**内置基元**——矩形（三角形和四边形）、立方体（四面体和六面体，后者采用二次基），以及通过 :class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen`"
" 生成的单位圆盘。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/basics.rst:260
#: ce7bf494fd264e2ebf3dfee3f41cc284
msgid ""
"**Hybrid meshes** — half the rectangle is meshed with triangles, the other "
"half with quadrilaterals, and a circular hole is punched in the interface. "
"``mesh.cells`` is a ``BufferDict`` keyed by element type, so all assemblers "
"iterate over both element types automatically."
msgstr ""
